@baseUrl = http://localhost:7331

### First read: source store -> Redis fill
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notes/note-1

### Second read: Redis hit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notes/note-1

### Create or replace a note and invalidate the cache
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "note-3",
  "title": "Fresh note",
  "body": "This note is written to the source store and its cache entry is invalidated."
}

### Read the new note: source store -> Redis fill
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notes/note-3

### Delete the note and invalidate the cache
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notes/note-3
